# Domain Naming Conventions

| Concept (ES) | Code name (EN) |
|---|---|
| Hipódromo | course |
| Carrera | race |
| Caballo | horse |
| Jinete | jockey |
| Entrenador | trainer |
| Participante en carrera | runner |
| Polla hípica | polla |
| Ticket / boleto | ticket |
| Combinación | combination |
| Selección | selection |
| Evento de juego | game_event |
| Enfrentamiento HvH | matchup |
| Apuesta | bet |
| Retiro de caballo | non_runner / withdrawal |
| Reemplazo | replacement |
| Premio | prize |
| Bote total | pool |
| Retención casa | house_cut |

# Project Contexts

- `BetPlace.Racing` — courses, races, horses, jockeys, trainers, runners
- `BetPlace.Games` — game_types, game_configs, game_events, game_event_races
- `BetPlace.Betting` — polla tickets, selections, combinations, hvh matchups/bets
- `BetPlace.Finance` — transactions (immutable ledger), balance management
- `BetPlace.Accounts` — users, authentication, roles (admin/bettor)
- `BetPlace.Api` — HTTP client, parser, sync_worker for horse racing API
